            {
              "content": "=You are a B2B outreach specialist.\n\nWrite a short personalized cold email based on the information below.\n\nName: {{ $json.name }}\nRole: {{ $json.role }}\nCompany: {{ $json.company }}\nEmail: {{ $json.email }}\nLinkedIn: {{ $json.linkedin }}\nCompany Website: {{ $json[\"company website\"] }}\n\nIntent Signal:\n{{ $json.intent_signal }}\n\nSummary:\n{{ $json.summary }}\n\nOpportunity:\n{{ $json.opportunity }}\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in this format:\n\n{\n \"name\":\"\",\n \"role\":\"\",\n \"company\":\"\",\n \"email\":\"\",\n \"linkedin\":\"\",\n \"company_website\":\"\",\n \"subject\":\"\",\n \"email_body\":\"\"\n}\n\nRules:\n- Keep the original values for name, role, company, email, linkedin, company_website.\n- Only generate subject and email_body.\n- Do not include markdown.\n- Do not include explanations.\n- Return JSON only."
            }
          ]
        },
